Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.52,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.81,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pair of sleeping skulls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.44,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hah! I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:14.98,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hold it against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.32,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryuk, wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.91,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come hang out with us \Nfor a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.00,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.88,DN Dialogue BG,,0,0,0,,Listen for the voice of God
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.42,DN Dialogue BG,,0,0,0,,and never guess you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.80,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do a thing, but he still got upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.96,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:39.22,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yagami, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:42.55,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please translate the following sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.44,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Follow the voice of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.81,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the blessings of the sea will become bountiful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.53,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there will be no storms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:03:00.91,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,Today, at approximately 11 a.m. \Nin Kanagawa Prefecture in Yokohama,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:05.54,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,the body of a man appearing to be about 30 years old \Nwas found in an apartment, covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.45,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,Kanagawa Police have opened a homicide investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.83,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,In other news...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:13.75,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,Today, shortly after noon, \Nin the Shibuya district of Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:18.21,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,a 25-year-old woman was gagged and killed by her live-in partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:23.51,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,35-year-old Tofuji Naoki is being \Nheld in custody charged with her murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.64,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Day in and day out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.44,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,the same thing over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.35,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.19,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's so ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.65,DN Thoughts,,0,1200,0,,This world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.65,DN Thoughts,,1200,0,0,,...is rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:49.45,DN Dialogue BG,,0,0,0,,Another is the extinction of many species of life on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.75,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! You went to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:54.75,DN Dialogue BG,,0,0,0,,Species are becoming extinct \Nat a faster rate than has occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.33,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a complete waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.08,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should've asked for a refund!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.75,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you {\i1}did{\i0} watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.16,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.92,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Literally translated as "a notebook of death."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.88,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,How to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:42.88,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,The human whose name is written in this note...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.05,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,shall die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.68,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,What a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.64,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,This is so sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:55.98,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's no different than a chain letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.82,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,"The human whose name is written in this note shall die?" C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:12.04,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Seriously... I must be going insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:19.46,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,There will be no effect when the face of \Nthe targetted person is not in the writer's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.17,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:24.47,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,people sharing the same name will not be affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:29.35,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death is written within \N40 seconds of writing the person's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.06,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,it will happen as it is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.52,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death is not specified, \Nthe person will simply die of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.77,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,After writing the cause of death, \Nin the next 6 minutes and 40 seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:41.27,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,details of the death should be written.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:46.95,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you can let people die peacefully or make them suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:51.08,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A prank this intricate isn't too bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.92,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Write their name and they die, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.75,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.81,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:24.28,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,If someone actually dies, \Ndoes that make me a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.45,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,No way. It'd never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:34.45,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,The assailant who killed six people yesterday at a busy shopping district in Shinjuku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:39.87,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,has now taken eight people hostage,\N including children and teachers, in this daycare center.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.87,0:06:44.05,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,The police have now identified the suspect as 42-year-old Otoharada Kurou, unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.26,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,The police will begin negotiations with the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.06,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,A heart attack in 40 seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.85,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.52,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,Well, that is not clear at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.11,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,You can't help but be worried for the hostages right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.27,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.82,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,This has been a report from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.32,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.61,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Mr. Hashimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:15.66,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm hoping for a quick resolution to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.54,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Oh well, nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.58,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,What did I expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.50,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.42,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,There seems to be something happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.13,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,The hostages are coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.80,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,They all seem to be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.34,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,And now it looks like the SWAT team is entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.01,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,Has the suspect been arrested?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.01,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:40.27,DN Announcements,,0,0,0,,We just received word that the suspect has died inside the daycare center!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.65,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,The suspect is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:43.98,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:49.90,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,The police are strongly denying that they shot the suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.66,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,Then could he have felt cornered and committed suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:57.79,DN Announcements BG,,0,0,0,,According to one of the hostages, \N"The suspect just suddenly collapsed."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.29,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,A heart attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.46,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.38,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,This is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.00,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.63,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.97,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost 6:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.26,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have cram school tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.72,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm getting ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:18.89,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,The Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.44,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's a long shot, but if this is the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.31,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,it's worth testing once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.48,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,In which case, the victim should probably be a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.61,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,But it can't be someone too infamous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:36.24,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,If they die, it's possible that \Ntheir deaths will be covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.20,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I need an immediate result.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.58,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryo baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.71,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it, Sudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.67,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lend me 'bout 2,000 yen, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.83,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.29,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Sudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.25,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You refusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.25,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Shall I kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:54.30,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,No, I'd better avoid people I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:55.76,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.14,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Why should I worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.47,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,If one or two people like him were to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.31,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,not a single soul would care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.23,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we can go to the arcade after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.86,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki, wanna party with some guys tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.98,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.74,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.70,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit, that stupid old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.91,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not here to pick me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.37,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It's sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.83,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Every single one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:26.79,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'd do society a favor \Nby killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.04,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.67,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fancy having some fun with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:36.55,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taku! You've got a beauty there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.68,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Shibuimaru Takuo. Shibutaku, for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.77,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang out with us for a while, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.39,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-{\alpha&HFF&\t(554,555,\alpha&H00&)}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.48,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.98,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.40,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, grab her. \NGet those clothes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.99,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.66,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.12,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.04,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.04,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Now let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.50,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,what'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.01,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.09,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taku! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.02,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,This... This settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.56,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,The Death Note is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.35,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.77,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.44,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just jumped out in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.57,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.99,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.55,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been five days since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.59,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.55,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.09,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Going out, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.18,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is barren everywhere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.48,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dropped my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.40,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really messed up big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:17.48,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, weren't you carrying around \Na second one behind the old man's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.49,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you lost both of 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.45,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do ya even know where ya dropped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.37,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.74,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.77,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.07,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're home early, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:11:59.94,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:03.20,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:03.86,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.54,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want the results of \Nthe national mock entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.12,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.12,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.54,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodness! Number one again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.59,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really did your best, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.84,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.59,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be studying, so don't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.84,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.34,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.22,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.89,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.10,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.35,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I already have what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.00,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.30,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:09.56,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who dropped that notebook was me, Ryuk, a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.02,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what I just saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.14,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're already aware that that's no ordinary notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.86,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,A Shinigami, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.66,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not shocked, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.54,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.66,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.54,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:42.13,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the Shinigami's Notebook was real,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.26,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but after seeing its results,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.43,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can act with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.76,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.85,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:58.31,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard of Death Notes getting down \Nto the Human World a few times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:02.78,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're the first one to use it to this extent in just five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.07,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most people would be too scared to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.11,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.49,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used a Death Note knowing it belonged to a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.08,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now the Shinigami's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.33,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what'll happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.37,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to take my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.88,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.42,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some fantasy you humans came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.59,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to do anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.39,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the Death Note lands in the Human World,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.72,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it belongs to the Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.60,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.14,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.31,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It belongs to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.90,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't want it, give it to some other human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.98,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you do that, all memory of \Nthe Death Note will be erased from your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.90,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So using the Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.24,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,doesn't come with a catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.66,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if anything, there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:56.79,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,only the fear and pain humans who \Nhave used the Death Note will experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.33,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when you die,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:05.13,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it falls to me to write your name in my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.59,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't think for a moment, that any human
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.72,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who's used the Death Note can go to Heaven, or Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.39,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.77,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll find out about it after you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.03,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.32,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.32,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:32.91,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.70,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought some apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.83,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're from our neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.00,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it so dark in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.04,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll ruin your eyesight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:41.71,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.71,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.50,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Mom can't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.80,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That notebook originally \Nbelonged to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.51,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since you're the one using it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.14,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,only you can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.35,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, my voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.18,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only you can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.39,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:03.02,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is a bond between Light the human and Ryuk the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.03,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.28,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.99,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.45,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.79,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apples in the Human World are awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.42,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:24.67,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Juicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.25,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.05,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:31.88,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just dropped the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:35.01,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you think you were chosen because you were smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.05,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.72,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just happened to fall around here and you just happened to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.43,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:47.40,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I wrote the explanation in English, \Nthe most popular language in the Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.65,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did you drop it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.95,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it was by mistake after you went to the trouble and wrote all those instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.11,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd I drop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.95,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.45,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:06.12,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is that Shinigami these days have a lot of time on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.96,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're either taking a nap or gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.76,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If others see you studiously scribbling names in the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.47,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they'll say, "What are you working so hard for?" and laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.72,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Writing names of other Shinigami doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.14,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since we live in the Shinigami Realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:25.98,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's no fun at all to kill people who live in the Human World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:31.19,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,744)}So I figured it'd be more fun to come down here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:36.28,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you sure wrote a lotta names.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:40.78,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why'd you write down the cause of death only for that guy who was hit by the truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:44.75,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without the cause of death written down, \Nthey all die of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:48.04,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the best thing about the Death Note, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:53.26,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can write down the names of the criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.63,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and slowly reduce the number of evil people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.43,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:02.43,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any fool can figure it out if someone is just "eliminating the bad guys."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:06.02,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want the world to know of my existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.40,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That there is someone passing judgment on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:16.28,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's the point in passing judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.57,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.41,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.12,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.04,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I didn't believe it at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.79,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.09,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,has the supernatural power to tempt people \Nto want to try it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.09,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I... I killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.93,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Two men...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.35,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I killed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.22,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Human lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.31,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,shouldn't be taken so lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:49.85,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Do I have the right \Nto judge people like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.23,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.86,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.07,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I've always thought about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.74,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,The world is rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.74,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Rotten people deserve to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:03.58,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.50,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Someone has to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:10.04,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Even if it means sacrificing \None's conscience and life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.25,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Things can't stay like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:17.09,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,If the Death Note had fallen into someone else's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:21.18,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,would they have had the resolve \Nto erase unwanted people from this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.10,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.93,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.31,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.93,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.23,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,only I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.81,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,And I will! With the Death Note!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.78,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,563)}I'll change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.57,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first I kept writing the names of criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:19.23,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as if I were cleaning up the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:23.32,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,932)}So that in time, no one would do evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.54,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While those guilty ones who truly deserved to be punished for their crimes die of heart attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:32.16,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,people who were immoral or harass others,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.42,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would slowly be erased through illness or accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:39.84,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the world would truly move in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:46.85,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I would create a new world of earnest, kind humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:51.06,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you'd be the only \Nfucked-up person left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.56,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.52,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:59.40,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm probably the best, most diligent honor student in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:03.28,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I will become...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.57,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the god of the new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:12.12,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.96,DN Thoughts,,0,0,0,,sure are interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:42.96,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entire world is watching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:47.09,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to see what happens to those who defy me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:48.17,DN Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L.
